public class Entity
extends java.util.AbstractMap<java.lang.String,java.lang.Object>
implements java.lang.Cloneable

Arbitrary entity object that stores all unknown field name/value pairs.

Subclasses can declare public fields for fields they do know, using the Java field name as the field name or the Name annotation to override the field name to use. Null field names are not allowed, but null field values are allowed.
